txt.en: 'Lheu Brenin imprisoned the emissary sent by Saruman.'
'The emissary from Isengard is locked up in the dungeon.'
'What do you Rangers know of Isengard and its master?'
'Saruman will not be pleased at the fate of the emissary he sent to us.'
'If we must fight all the clans of Dunland, we will do so. And we will triumph!'
'No Wizard will command the Falcon, not while Lheu Brenin lives.'
